#ELLEFashion: Hell hath no fury like a woman scorned and no one does revenge better than a woman. Elegant, powerful, and unforgettable, the revenge dress is far more than a fashion moment. It stands as a reminder that women are not defined by the men of their past. From Princess Diana’s iconic off-shoulder black dress to recently in fiction world Maddy Perez’s internet breaking risqué green look, these outfits transformed heartbreak into drama and style. Swipe through some of the iconic revenge dresses in the history of pop culture.
